<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Sweicker, uns
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                            <add>die nü bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ichs</ex></expan>, <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> sind</add>, wol gesagt und zu wissen
                        getan, wie ir in gen <add><expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan></add>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> in
                        iren <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>vast</add>
<expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewesen seit, des wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan></add> gar fleissiklich
                                <expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und
                        <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in fürbaz aber <add>in
                                    <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> iren
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gunstige hilff und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, beweisen wöllet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
